  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>From Bangkok International Suvarnabhumi Airport: Take the Airport Link from Suvarnabhumi Airport to Makkasan station. Then connect with the MRT network at Phetchburi station to Hua Lampong station. Then take a tuk tuk for only 3 minutes to Chilli Bangkok Hostel at Soi Charoen Krung 37. How to find the hotel: turn into Soi (pedestrian street) Chareon Krung 37 and walk about 25 m until the end. Then turn right 2 m and turn left and the hotel will be visible.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>Built in 2010, this 25-room club resort is the perfect choice for the single traveller or travellers who come with their favourite 'buddy'. In addition to a lobby area with 24-hour reception and check-out services, facilities available to guests at this air-conditioned establishment include a bar, wireless Internet access and a laundry service (fees apply). Guests arriving by car can leave their vehicles in the hotel car park for an extra charge.</Text>
  </Description>
